ecoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Pharrell-Williams.-CREDIT_-Stephane-Cardinale-Corbis_Corbis-via-Getty-Image.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Pharrell-Williams.-CREDIT_-Stephane-Cardinale-Corbis_Corbis-via-Getty-Image-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Pharrell-Williams.-CREDIT_-Stephane-Cardinale-Corbis_Corbis-via-Getty-Image-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Pharrell-Williams.-CREDIT_-Stephane-Cardinale-Corbis_Corbis-via-Getty-Image-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Pharrell-Williams.-CREDIT_-Stephane-Cardinale-Corbis_Corbis-via-Getty-Image-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Pharrell-Williams.-CREDIT_-Stephane-Cardinale-Corbis_Corbis-via-Getty-Image-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pharrell-williams">法瑞尔·威廉姆斯 (Pharrell Williams)</a>分享了一首来自他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pharrell-announces-his-biopic-will-be-made-out-of-lego-3578112">即将上映的同名乐高传记片</a>原声带的新歌《Piece By Piece》。看看下面。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pharrell-williams-morgan-neville-interview-trailer-lego-piece-by-piece-3762433">法瑞尔·威廉姆斯向我们讲述他的乐高传记片《逐片》：“这对我来说是一次奇妙的历史经历”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位音乐家将在摩根·内维尔 (Morgan Neville) 执导的新电影中记录他的生活和职业生涯，该电影将于 10 月 11 日在美国上映，11 月 8 日在英国上映。这部电影将深入探讨他与查德·雨果在制作人团体<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-neptunes">“海王星”</a>中的时光，以及与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/snoop-dogg">史努比狗狗</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gwen-stefani">格温·史蒂芬妮</a>等人的合作。</p><p> 《Piece By Piece》是电影原声带的初体验，以威廉姆斯本人就读的安妮公主高中精彩行进骑士队为特色。</p><p>这首歌讲述了威廉姆斯的职业道德和成为音乐家的动机，同时巧妙地引用了著名的塑料积木。 “<em>寻找并打破奇迹/我们不断堆叠，高，高，高</em>，”他唱道。 “<em>一点一点，一点一点，一点一点，一点一点</em>。”看看下面。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="一点一点（官方音频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/bu59Z7J80Pk?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>威廉姆斯担任联合制片人的这部电影除了讲述他自己的音乐行业历程外，还将由他过去著名的合作者客串，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jay-z">Jay Z</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gwen-stefani">格温·史蒂芬尼</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kendrick-lamar">肯德里克·拉马尔</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/snoop-dogg">史努比狗狗</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/justin-timberlake">贾斯汀·汀布莱克</a>和更多的。</p><p>本周早些时候，据透露， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/daft-punk-to-feature-in-pharrell-williams-lego-biopic-piece-by-piece-3790136">傻朋克将出现在这部电影中，</a>因为他们的名字出现在最近分享的官方电影海报上。这对法国电子二人组与 Williams 合作制作了<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/daft-punk-get-lucky-song-summer-five-years-2297009">2013 年的热门单曲“Get Lucky”</a> 。</p><p>本月早些时候<em>，《Piece by Piece》</em>的全球首映拉开了特柳赖德电影节的序幕。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pharrell-williams-morgan-neville-interview-trailer-lego-piece-by-piece-3762433">在 6 月接受<em>NME</em>采访时</a>，威廉姆斯解释了这部电影“对我来说是一次奇妙的历史经历”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_QpYl6JNx7/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div s